# 5. 爆走！こはねオオカミ！

Kohane: Wait!
An: Wh-Why's that thing chasing after me?! Is this entire place supposed to be the haunted house?!
An: I-I've just gotta keep running...!
Kohane: Huff... Huff... An's too fast...! I can't catch her...
Rin: <And there's a ton of people... It's so easy to lose sight of her...!>
Student: Huh?! What's that thing?!
Student: Did one of the other classes make that?
Rin: <Uh oh... People are gonna probably freak out if they see me, so I'm gonna hide for a bit...!>
Rin: <Aha!!!>
Rin: <Kohane! An just ducked into that classroom!>
Kohane: That one?! An!
Saki: Oh, hello! Welcome to the Flufftacular Animal Cafe☆...
Saki: *Scream*
Saki: I-I-I-I-Ichi!!! Help! Something scary just walked in!!!
Ichika: Huh? Whoa!! Wh-What is that...?! A zombie wolf...?!
Haruka: That is pretty scary...
Guest: Whoa, that thing's pretty terrifying...! Is it supposed to be some kind of zombified animal?
Guest: Does it work here or something? But it looks pretty grotesque!
Kohane: S-Sorry! I'm not here to hurt anyone! I just came in to...!
Haruka: Hm...?
Haruka: That voice... Kohane?
Kohane: H-Haruka...!
Haruka: (It is her. And she sounds pretty worried. I wonder what's going on.)
Boy: *Cry* I'm scared!
Haruka: But first, we need to calm everyone down...
Haruka: Hey, Wolfie! I think you're in the wrong forest!
Haruka: Shouldn't you be at Class 1-A? Are you here to advertise your haunted house? It's called “Little Red Riding Hood and the Young Goats' Slightly Scary Forest Adventure”, right?
Kohane: Huh...?! Y-Yes!
Kohane: Class 1-A is doing a haunted house! I-It's really fun, so we hope you'll stop by later!
Saki: Th-Thank goodness...! They're just here to advertise!
Ichika: I wasn't expecting another class to surprise us like that.
Haruka: Class 1-A's haunted house is meant to be enjoyable for everyone. You don't have to be a hardcore thrill seeker to have fun, so please check it out.
Guest: Oh, it was just a different class advertising... Still, that mask looked pretty scary...
Guest: Let's go check it out afterwards!
Kohane: Th-Thank you so much, Haruka...!
Haruka: You're welcome, but... Why did you rush in...? Oh...
Haruka: Is this where you agreed to meet An?
Haruka: She jumped in a second ago and ran out after she saw you follow her. I think she went towards the AV room...
Kohane: ...! Thank you, Haruka! I promise to pay you back later for this!
Haruka: Wait, Kohane! If you run out with that thing on your head...!
Third Kobuta Sister: “...Mr. Okami turned himself in to the police and repaid his debt to society!”
Eldest Kobuta Sister: “The end.”
Emu: Hehe. We did it, Honami! That went really well!
Honami: Yes, it did! Thank you for working so much with me during practices, Emu.
Emu: Huh?
Honami: Eep...!
Kohane: (Oh no! I forgot...! This is where Emu's class is doing their show...!)
Kohane: I-I'm so sorry!!!
Spectator: Wh-What was that...?! It looked like a horrifying wolf...
Spectator: Was it supposed to appear at the end of the show...?!
Honami: Th-That wasn't in the script, was it...? Emu, what should we do...?!
Emu: “Mr. Okami has been rehabilitated! However, this world is full of other baddies and evil creatures... Like mean Mr. Wolf...!”
Emu: “We, the three Kobuta Sisters, will continue fighting to put them all back on the right path!”
Emu: “You can do it! We believe in you! I hope you'll all keep rooting for us!”
Spectator: Huh...?! Oh, now I get it. That's how it's supposed to end.
Spectator: So the grand finale was only the beginning... That's pretty cool...
Honami: Th-That was amazing, Emu!
Emu: Hehe. Thanks! But what happened to Mr. Wolf...?
Airi: Thanks for your purchase! We hope you enjoy the rest of the festival!
Shizuku: Hehe. It was so nice of Ena and the others to stop by.
Airi: Alright, let's keep this momentum going by selling even more!
Rin: <Sorry about that, Kohane! Seriously, where'd An go...?>
Kohane: I don't see her either... Do you think she's still in the building?
Rin: <Kohane, watch out! You might trip on one of these signs!>
Kohane: Okay, I'll be... Wah!!
Kohane: *Sob* Just as you warned me...
Airi: H-Hey, are you okay...?!
Kohane: Sh-Shizuku?! Airi?!
Kohane: (Huh...?! I ended up in front of their sweets stall...?!)
Guest: Wh-What is that thing?
Guest: It cut in line too...
Kohane: O-Oh no...! I'm causing another big fuss...!
Shizuku: That voice... Kohane, is that you? What a cute wolf's head♪
Kohane: C-Cute...? I'm not sure how cute it is, but... I'm so sorry...! I didn't mean to cause you so much trouble...!
Airi: That's all good. I mean, accidents happen. Let's just say a wolf appeared and ate some of our things...
Airi: Hmm... Oh, I know!
Airi: Help! There's a wolf here!
Kohane: Wh-What?
Airi: That wolf gobbled up all the sweets we had lined up on here!
Airi: At this rate, Shizuku, it's gonna eat everything!
Shizuku: ...! Yes, you're right♪ If Mr. Wolf likes them so much, I suppose it means they're just that delicious♪
Girl: Oh, she's right...! They look delicious and smell wonderfully sweet! Hang on... These look like pot stickers!
Kohane: Th-That was incredible...! It's so amazing what idols can do...!
Airi: You should be fine now. Just watch where you step, okay, Kohane?
Kohane: Th-Thank you very much! I will!
Kohane: Oh, by the way... Have you seen An anywhere?
Shizuku: An? No, I can't say we have...
Kohane: I see... But thank you anyway. And again, I'm sorry! Now, if you'll excuse me!
Minori: No...! I can't find Kohane anywhere!
Minori: She should stick out like a sore thumb too... Oh!
Shiho: Minori? What are you doing here?
Minori: Sh-Shiho!! Are you already done checking your equipment for the night festival?!
Shiho: Yeah, I was on my way back to see if I could help with anything... Did something happen while I was gone?
Minori: Oh, um... The thing is...
Shiho: Wow, that all really happened...?
Minori: Yeah... Kohane was really looking forward to hanging out with her teammates too...
Shiho: Let's split up and try to find her. You go back inside. I'll look around the courtyard...
Shizuku: We have homemade sweets here... Hm? Shii!
Shiho: Sh-Shizuku...? Oh, right, this is your class' stall.
Minori: Airi! Shizuku! Did you happen to see a zombie wolf run by here?!
Shizuku: A zombie wolf? Do you mean Kohane? I think she went that way to go back inside the building...
Minori: Really?! Thank you so much, Shizuku! Let's go, Shiho!
Airi: W-Wait, hold up! What happened exactly?!
Minori: S-Sorry, no time to talk! I'll explain later...!
Shiho: Oh, Shizuku. Can you send me a message if you see her again?
Shizuku: *Gasp* Yes, of course! Anything you ask, Shii!
Airi: I still can't figure out what's going on... I feel like we should help if they're that desperate to find her...
Shizuku: I feel the same way. Let's try asking our classmates to tell us if they see... Oh!
Shizuku: Asahina! Sorry, can we ask you a favor?
Mafuyu: ...? Hinomori...?
